creator: LanaComplex
descriptionHtml:
Hello my dear girls! Lana - is me.
I am a pharmacist by profession, and 10 years ago I decided to leave the pharmacy business and concentrate on what was close to my heart – developing my new cosmetic production line.

🌙I know what HAIR and SKIN need.
🧾Pharmacist for education.
✨Fairy of creams by vocation 💗🤍💗

Why the name Complex? Complex - for me brings out a set of interconnected actions for body and hair care, those actions complimenting and strengthening each other, all united in being organic. For me it's a way of life.

I am very glad to welcome you to this new space LanaComplex. With it, I start a new chapter of my soap and cream creativity on a new platform. Let this place become for each of you a guide, an ally, an assistant and just a friend that you sometimes miss. 😎

Know that my door is always open! Do not hesitate to contact me and ask me questions or offer suggestions and any other feedback so I can hear each and every one of you👌

For those who meet me here for the first time, I think my Stories in Instagram🤗 are the quickest way to get to know me and what I attempt to achieve with Lana Complex. You can see all the stages and intricacies of my processes and know that I do this not for the sake of a beautiful picture, but for the sake of your trust!

What else do you need to know about me? I can not imagine a comfortable life without natural soap, shampoo and cream. For me, this is the minimum care package for every day for complete happiness (cleansing, nutrition) of skin and hair for the whole family, and especially with newborns or toddler of any age!

To be pure - You do not have to poison yourself with suffocating synthetic aromas of shower gel, which then peels off the skin in flakes. Same with the Hair Shampoo – your hair will not grow strong when your scalp absorbs harsh, aggressive surfactants and any number of associated “usefulness” that is designed only to keep the emulsion and aroma in their marketable form for several years.

In contrast, the aromas in LanaComplex products often use only essential oils, and if my soul asks for something delicious - then only aromatic extracts, which, like all other components, are purchased from Aroma-zone in France (Paris).

I use herbal extracts to produce healthy soaps using a variety of preparatory processes that make the varieties of soap noticeably different to each other. Each one also carries specific functions: to be as delicate and soft as possible or to provide anti-inflammatory qualities, to cleanse and to soothe. It is up to you to choose, it is a matter of taste and personal preference.

Thank you to everyone who has been faithful to LanaComplex for so many years! Thank you to everyone who left, but then came back again - it's priceless! Thank you to everyone who is simply a spectator of how a unique manufacturer of cosmetics and natural soap LanaComplex keeps growing from a small soap maker 💛💙
